   <pre>glad for you michael i know last time we talked you were excited about going to texas... glad to see now that things have worked out for you...
i really hate you have to sale the bus and your parts but sometimes things like this happen and well its for the good you being a family man and all.
seen the movie last night cheaper by the dozen with steve martin and thought of you and your family moving to texas.it was a bus movie as well or started out that way.... we'll miss your post but we will see you around again you have vw in your blood...
